data.title: Population: Hebei: Xingtai: Xingtai
data.meta_description: Population: Hebei: Xingtai: Xingtai data was reported at 363.000 Person th in Dec 2019. This records an increase from the previous number of 361.708 Person th for Dec 2018. Population: Hebei: Xingtai: Xingtai data is updated yearly, averaging 362.354 Person th (Median) from Dec 2004 to 2019, with 16 observations. The data reached an all-time high of 474.151 Person th in 2009 and a record low of 330.300 Person th in 2017. Population: Hebei: Xingtai: Xingtai data remains active status in CEIC and is reported by National Bureau of Statistics. The data is categorized under China Premium Database’s Socio-Demographic – Table CN.GJ: Population: County Level Region.
